 b.io

SUMMARY:Faisal Romshoo — Deformations of calibrations

DESCRIPTION:Speaker: Faisal Romshoo\nTitle: Deformations of calibrations\n\

 nWe will look at a criterion for unobstructedness for calibrations and see 

 when the corresponding moduli spaces form smooth manifolds\, following the 

 approach by Goto in https://arxiv.org/abs/math/0112197

