 hub.io

SUMMARY:Faisal Romshoo — Deformations of calibrations\, II

DESCRIPTION:Speaker: Faisal Romshoo\nTitle: Deformations of calibrations\, 

 II\n\nWe will continue where we left off last time\, completing the proof o

 f when the obstructions for the calibrations vanish. If time permits\, we w

 ill go through the proof of the fact that if an orbit is metrical\, ellipti

 c and topological\, then the corresponding moduli space is a smooth manifol

 d. 

